{"tid":1220142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳智思：不能再加劇對立　政府要盤算重新解說或諮詢","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:32:10.000Z","uid":50386,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d88f62d5c4dc563bec67e8b4873ee84c8b24439f","tid":1220142,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"立法會大會會議連續三日押後開會，未能恢復二讀修訂《逃犯條例》草案。行政會議召集人陳智思表示，經過星期三的大衝突後，現時不可能在對立面如此激烈下繼續討論，難度很高，認為近日不能再加劇對立，因此政府要盤算如何處理，包括重新解說、諮詢等。<br />\n<br />\n至於應否急於在立法會今屆會期內處理，陳智思在本台節目《千禧年代》說，要視乎是否有信心通過修例，但他不想因一條草案令議會停頓，仍有其他包括房屋等議題需要跟進。<br />\n<br />\n陳智思承認自己低估了商界對修例的反響，最初認為法案並無問題，但後來可能政府的解說不足，很多令人恐懼的消息出來，令商界擔心，而可能其他參與修例的人，亦無預計反響這麼大。至於自己是否需要問責，陳智思說，由行政長官決定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e7422ec1ca36891af644424ecb73a1944c1dff","tid":1220142,"uid":31946,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"解你老母 諮你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係撤回 一係繼續"},{"pid":"80e2a5d2ca551aa1684245a306d01e7fa4651b3c","tid":1220142,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"繼續係解說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7069480d13fdfbce4b0d0ce109d9a7a667314ad3","tid":1220142,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:55:24.000Z","msg":"廢話 慳返啖氣"},{"pid":"4b10b599b17a6a192e907b8d0768a0120c032552","tid":1220142,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:55:29.000Z","msg":"解您老母陳智思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c94bba474de6546292e3a600d8b20fa1af5bee9","tid":1220142,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:56:05.000Z","msg":"係要撤回"},{"pid":"92e9827990f50bd6bf8aab49cd797745a1b0df70","tid":1220142,"uid":26327,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:58:36.000Z","msg":"屌 , 應該好快會話 <br />\n<br />\n建制派成功爭取林鄭撤回方案，<br />\n<br />\n建制派與政府對話 才是解決方法， 強烈譴責泛民等暴力人士<br />\n<br />\nDLLM !!!"},{"pid":"44a776bb2fadb655b62a428b13507ec59083b3f6","tid":1220142,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"呢條茂里好似想趁亂上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}